article_text:

article_metadata.description: How do you feel now that the partial government shutdown is over and the debt ceiling has been raised? We're looking for your reaction. Post your comments below, on the Morning Express Facebook page or tweet @RobinMeade. She'll be reading some of your comments on the air.The partial government shutdown is over.
article_metadata.author: Yacov Freedman
